 is\nshown for wide ranges of the problem's parameters. Estimated formula for the\nborder of convergence area of the iterative process in the space of system\nparameters is obtained. Also we have provided justification of the analytical\niterative method solution for Cauchy problem for the 3D Navier-Stokes\nequations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Jan 2011 19:46:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 15 Jan 2011 21:20:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 9 Jul 2011 02:38:04 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 15 Jul 2011 04:31:16 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Sat, 24 Sep 2011 03:07:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-09-27"}
