mmarized. These data are used to argue that the high spins of\nat least some of these black holes are natal, and that the presence or absence\nof relativistic jets in accreting black holes is not entirely determined by the\nspin of the black hole.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Jan 2011 21:00:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 29 Jan 2011 18:09:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-20"}
